[
    {
        "startTime": 8593,
        "endTime": 11011,
        "text": "So, of all the stadiums of 2019 Rugby World Cup,..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 11100,
        "endTime": 14718,
        "text": "...this is by far the smallest, with a capacity of 16 odd thousand seats,..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 15035,
        "endTime": 16764,
        "text": "...but by far the most important."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 16967,
        "endTime": 18009,
        "text": "We're here at Kamaishi,..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 18098,
        "endTime": 21433,
        "text": "...the Kamaishi Unosumai Recovery Memorial Stadium."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 21611,
        "endTime": 24587,
        "text": "This stadium is being specifically built to help this city..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 24672,
        "endTime": 25500,
        "text": "...get back on its feet."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 26029,
        "endTime": 27195,
        "text": "And if you look up here,..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 27281,
        "endTime": 29570,
        "text": "...you can actually see all the valleys..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 29692,
        "endTime": 32017,
        "text": "...where the wall of water would have come straight through here."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 32115,
        "endTime": 35662,
        "text": "I can't even picture a 40-meter wall of seawater..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 35773,
        "endTime": 37483,
        "text": "...just rushing straight in through here."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 37595,
        "endTime": 39659,
        "text": "And this is literally where the school used to be,..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 40064,
        "endTime": 43311,
        "text": "...and I ran up to that hill over there to get to safety."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 43495,
        "endTime": 44645,
        "text": "It would have just been terrifying..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 44769,
        "endTime": 48614,
        "text": "...and you can't even imagine the sheer terror of that coming through here."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 50489,
        "endTime": 53717,
        "text": "Seeing the city being rebuilt for the 2019 Rugby World Cup..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 53816,
        "endTime": 55715,
        "text": "...is a truly humbling experience..."
    },
    {
        "startTime": 55827,
        "endTime": 58609,
        "text": "...and I can't wait to see the games played here."
    }
]